        <div class="feat-body">
          <span class="feat-num">11</span>
          <h3 itemprop="name">Role-based Access Control</h3>
          <p itemprop="description">Granular permissions for every module and action. Secure your app with fine-tuned access policies.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="feat-item" itemprop="itemListElement" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem">
        <meta itemprop="position" content="12">
        <div class="feat-ic" style="background:var(--cyan-bg);color:var(--cyan)"><i class="fa-solid fa-database"></i></div>
        <div class="feat-body">
          <span class="feat-num">12</span>
          <h3 itemprop="name">Data Migration</h3>
          <p itemprop="description">Migrate from legacy systems, Excel, or other software. Clean, validated data transfer with zero downtime.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="pwhy">
  <div class="pwhy-inner">
    <h2>Why Choose Softwaller</h2>
    <p class="sub">We don't just build software — we build solutions that grow with your business.</p>
    <div class="pwhy-grid">
      <div class="pwhy-item">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-pencil-ruler"></i>
        <div><h3>Built for Your Workflow</h3><p>Custom-designed to match how your team actually works, not the other way around.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="pwhy-item">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-dots"></i>
        <div><h3>Scale as You Grow</h3><p>Architecture designed to handle 500+ concurrent users without breaking a sweat.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="pwhy-item">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-mobile-screen"></i>
        <div><h3>Mobile Ready</h3><p>Access from any device, anywhere, anytime. Your office travels with you.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="pwhy-item">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-plug"></i>
        <div><h3>Integration Ready</h3><p>Connect with Tally, WhatsApp, payment gateways, and more out of the box.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="pwhy-item">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-headset"></i>
        <div><h3>Ongoing Support</h3><p>3 months free support plus AMC options after go-live. We're always here for you.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="pwhy-item">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved"></i>
        <div><h3>Data Security</h3><p>Role-based access, encryption, and audit trails keep your business data safe.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="p-related">
