      <div class="faq-answer">We choose stack per project: .NET 9, Blazor, ASP.NET Core, React, MAUI, and SQL Server for enterprise apps; Node.js, React Native, Next.js, and PostgreSQL for SaaS-style apps. We always pick proven, long-term maintainable tech.</div>
    </details>
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>Do we own the source code?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer">Yes. After full payment, source code, design assets, and IP fully belong to you. We provide signed code escrow if required. You can host it anywhere, hire any developer, and modify it freely.</div>
